<Author>bobsmith465
<Content>Simply the Best! The Estrel is simply my favorite hotel. I come to Berlin every few months for a convention, and always chose to stay at this hotel. The prices are VERY fair compared to the other hotel prices in Berlin. The hotel features everything I need, restaurants, bars, and even live entertainment. The location next to the water and the train station provides easy access to the city center within 10 minutes. I would recommend this Hotel to all business travelers and families looking for a great vacation. Also, the Hotel is recently upgrading all of its rooms and suites. I slept in one of the new rooms, and I have to say they are great. The new style is more Asian-European, with bamboo wood, and art. VERY VERY NICE! Keep it up Estrel, you are simply the best! 
