<Content>Terrible Place I stayed here because of the convention that was located in this hotel. What a mistake. There was nothing good about place, nothing. Location, horrible bordering on dangerous. Make no mistake, you are a captive here ant they charge for simple thigns like a glass of water accordingly. And that's only when you can get serive to begin with.Service, slow and often times simply unavailable.Rooms, The worst. This place is like an old Russian prsion or something. Ugly and uncomfortable. No aircon and huge slabs of concrete walls to keep all that wonderful heat inside. Innaproporiate for the business traveller.Conference Rooms, what a joke ! Some were completely slapped together with temporary walls and often there were columns and blockages in the rooms. No two rooms were the same. A real mismash of styles and locations.Don't stay here under any circumstances. 
